OL,6,FEury was in the country to train in
OL,7,FMuay Thai boxing and to find new
OL,8,Finspiration and ingredients for his
OL,9,Fbusiness Gorilla Thai Kitchen, which
OL,10,Fhas two sites in Bristol.
OL,12,FLong-time friend of Eury, Harry
OL,13,FBradford, said that the fundraiser
OL,14,Fwill help to remove "a level of stress
OL,15,Fand pressure" from Ricky and his
OL,16,Ffamily, with his medical bills already
OL,17,Fsurpassing #100,000.
