OL,6,FWhile Eury's condition has improved
OL,7,Fwith him having regained
OL,8,Fconsciousness, he remains in Thailand
OL,9,Fas his condition means he is unable to
OL,10,Ffly back home due to the bleed and
OL,11,Fswelling on his brain.
OL,13,FHis insurance ran out the day before
OL,14,Fhe was hit, which means his family are
OL,15,Fcovering medical bills which have
OL,16,Fquickly piled up.
OL,18,FAn online fundraiser set up to help
OL,19,Fcover his medical expenses has raised
OL,20,Fmore than #30,000.
