OL,6,FHowever, the cost of his care has
OL,7,Falready surpassed that figure.
OL,9,FHarry Bradford said: "He really wants
OL,10,Fto come home, that's his main priority
OL,11,Fat the moment.
OL,13,F"He's feeling frustrated that he's
OL,14,Fstuck on the other side of the world.
OL,15,FHis son is here, a lot of his family
OL,16,Fare here, his close friends are here.
