OL,6,F"His life is here, his life has been
OL,7,Fput on hold for a number of months
OL,8,Falready and it's going to be a lot
OL,9,Flonger than that probably until he's
OL,10,Fback and fighting fit.
OL,12,F"He's more positive that he's healing
OL,13,Fa bit better but he still has bleeding
OL,14,Fin his brain and swelling which needs
OL,15,Fto go down before he can get on a
OL,16,Fplane.
OL,18,F"(Ricky)'s always been that person who
OL,19,Ftalk to everyone and looks after those
OL,20,Faround him.
